OL,3,C'I saw nothing': Bill Clinton
OL,4,Ctestifies about relationship with
OL,5,CJeffrey Epstein
OL,7,FIt is the first time a former
OL,8,Fpresident has been compelled to give
OL,9,Fevidence to a Congressional committee,
OL,10,Fand it comes a day after his wife,
OL,11,Fformer Secretary of State Hillary
OL,12,FClinton, made her own deposition. ITV
OL,13,FNews US Correspondent Dan Rivers
OL,14,Freports.
OL,16,FFormer US President Bill Clinton has
OL,17,Fsaid he "did nothing wrong" and saw no
OL,18,Fsigns of Jeffrey Epstein's abuse, in
OL,19,Fhis opening statement to US lawmakers
OL,20,Fabout his relationship with the
OL,21,Fconvicted paedophile.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
