OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772337174
OL,3,C'I saw nothing': Bill Clinton
OL,4,Ctestifies about relationship with
OL,5,CJeffrey Epstein
OL,7,FClinton is testifying in a closed-door
OL,8,Fdeposition in Chappaqua, New York,
OL,9,Fwhich marks the first time a former
OL,10,Fpresident has been compelled to
OL,11,Ftestify to Congress.
OL,13,F"I saw nothing, and I did nothing
OL,14,Fwrong," the former Democratic
OL,15,Fpresident said in a statement he
OL,16,Fshared on social media.
OL,18,FIt came a day after his wife, former
OL,19,FSecretary of State Hillary Clinton,
OL,20,Fsat with lawmakers for her own
OL,21,Fdeposition.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1772337174
OL,3,C'I saw nothing': Bill Clinton
OL,4,Ctestifies about relationship with
OL,5,CJeffrey Epstein
OL,7,FHillary Clinton also denied any
OL,8,Fknowledge of Epstein's crimes and said
OL,9,Fshe had never met him.
OL,11,FBut Bill Clinton will have to answer
OL,12,Fquestions on a well-documented
OL,13,Frelationship with Epstein and his
OL,14,Fformer girlfriend Ghislaine Maxwell,
OL,15,Feven if it was from the late 1990s and
OL,16,Fearly 2000s.
OL,18,FAppearing in the Epstein files is not
OL,19,Fan indication of wrongdoing, and
OL,20,FClinton has denied any knowledge of,
OL,21,For involvement in, Epstein's crimes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
