OL,3,C'I saw nothing': Bill Clinton
OL,4,Ctestifies about relationship with
OL,5,CJeffrey Epstein
OL,7,FHillary Clinton said on Thursday that
OL,8,Fshe expected her husband to testify
OL,9,Fthat he had no knowledge of Epstein's
OL,10,Fsexual abuse at the time they knew
OL,11,Feach other.
OL,13,FRepublicans were relishing the
OL,14,Fopportunity to scrutinise the former
OL,15,FDemocratic president under oath.
OL,17,F"No one's accusing anyone of any
OL,18,Fwrongdoing, but I think the American
OL,19,Fpeople have a lot of questions,"
OL,20,FRepublican Rep. James Comer, the chair
OL,21,Fof the House Oversight Committee, said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
