OL,3,C'I saw nothing': Bill Clinton
OL,4,Ctestifies about relationship with
OL,5,CJeffrey Epstein
OL,7,FRepublicans have wanted to question
OL,8,FBill Clinton about Epstein for years,
OL,9,Fespecially as conspiracy theories
OL,10,Farose following Epstein's 2019 suicide
OL,11,Fin a New York jail cell while he faced
OL,12,Fsex trafficking charges.
OL,14,FThose calls reached a fever pitch late
OL,15,Flast year when several photos of the
OL,16,Fformer president surfaced in the
OL,17,FDepartment of Justice's first release
OL,18,Fof case files on Epstein and Maxwell,
OL,19,Fa British socialite who was convicted
OL,20,Fof sex trafficking in December 2021
OL,21,Fbut maintains she's innocent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
