OL,3,C'I saw nothing': Bill Clinton
OL,4,Ctestifies about relationship with
OL,5,CJeffrey Epstein
OL,7,FBill Clinton was photographed on a
OL,8,Fplane seated alongside a woman, whose
OL,9,Fface is redacted, with his arm around
OL,10,Fher. Another photo showed Clinton and
OL,11,FMaxwell in a pool with another person
OL,12,Fwhose face was redacted.
OL,14,FEpstein also visited the White House
OL,15,Fseveral times during Clinton's
OL,16,Fpresidency, and the pair later made
OL,17,Fseveral international trips together
OL,18,Ffor their humanitarian work.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
