OL,3,C'I saw nothing': Bill Clinton
OL,4,Ctestifies about relationship with
OL,5,CJeffrey Epstein
OL,7,FDemocratic Representative Robert
OL,8,FGarcia says they deserve serious
OL,9,Fanswers from former president Bill
OL,10,FClinton and that they want to hear
OL,11,Ffrom anyone who knows about Epstein,
OL,12,F'no matter how powerful they are'
OL,14,FComer claimed the committee has
OL,15,Fcollected evidence that Epstein
OL,16,Fvisited the White House 17 times and
OL,17,Fthat Bill Clinton flew on Epstein's
OL,18,Faeroplane 27 times.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
