OL,3,C'I saw nothing': Bill Clinton
OL,4,Ctestifies about relationship with
OL,5,CJeffrey Epstein
OL,7,FIn the lead-up to the deposition, Bill
OL,8,FClinton has insisted he had limited
OL,9,Fknowledge about Epstein and was
OL,10,Funaware of any sexual abuse he
OL,11,Fcommitted.
OL,13,F"I think the chronology of the
OL,14,Fconnection that he had with Epstein
OL,15,Fended several years before anything
OL,16,Fabout Epstein's criminal activities
OL,17,Fcame to light," Hillary Clinton said
OL,18,Fat the conclusion of her deposition
OL,19,FThursday.
