OL,3,C'I saw nothing': Bill Clinton
OL,4,Ctestifies about relationship with
OL,5,CJeffrey Epstein
OL,7,FComer has pledged extensive
OL,8,Fquestioning of the former president.
OL,9,FHe claimed that Hillary Clinton had
OL,10,Frepeatedly deferred questions about
OL,11,FEpstein to her husband.
OL,13,FThe committee was working to publish a
OL,14,Ftranscript and video recording of her
OL,15,Fdeposition.
