OL,3,C'I saw nothing': Bill Clinton
OL,4,Ctestifies about relationship with
OL,5,CJeffrey Epstein
OL,7,FDemocrats, who have supported the push
OL,8,Fto get answers from Bill Clinton, are
OL,9,Farguing that it sets a precedent that
OL,10,Fshould also apply to President Donald
OL,11,FTrump, a Republican who had his own
OL,12,Frelationship with Epstein.
OL,14,F"I think that President Trump needs to
OL,15,Fman up, get in front of this committee
OL,16,Fand answer the questions and stop
OL,17,Fcalling this investigation a hoax,"
OL,18,Fsaid Representative Robert Garcia, the
OL,19,Ftop Democrat on the committee, on
OL,20,FFriday.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@cO]
