OL,3,C'I saw nothing': Bill Clinton
OL,4,Ctestifies about relationship with
OL,5,CJeffrey Epstein
OL,7,FComer has pushed back on that idea,
OL,8,Fsaying that Trump has answered
OL,9,Fquestions on Epstein from the press.
OL,11,FTrump has repeatedly denied any
OL,12,Fwrongdoing.
